# Styling and CSS Conventions

## Color Scheme
The project uses a **dark theme** with these primary colors:
- **Background**: `#121212` (main background)
- **Text**: `#fff` (primary text), `#bbbbbb` (secondary text)
- **Accent**: `#00a2ff` (hover states)
- **Highlight**: `#60d394` (special highlights)

## Typography
- **Primary Font**: `'Rubik', 'Inter', sans-serif`
- **Font Weights**: 300-900 (Rubik), 100-900 (Public Sans)
- **Font Sizes**: Use rem units for scalability
- **Line Height**: 1.5 for body text, adjust for headings

## Layout Patterns

### CSS Grid Usage
```css
.navbar {
	display: grid;
	grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
	align-items: center;
}
```

### Flexbox Usage
```css
.profile-container {
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	align-items: center;
}
```

### Responsive Design
- **Mobile First**: Start with mobile styles, add desktop with `@media`
- **Breakpoint**: `768px` for mobile/desktop transition
- **Mobile Navigation**: Full-screen overlay with smooth transitions

## Animation Patterns

### Keyframe Animations
```css
@keyframes slideFromTop {
	0% {
		transform: translateY(-30px);
		opacity: 20%;
	}
	100% {
		transform: translateY(0);
		opacity: 100%;
	}
}
```

### Transition Usage
```css
.desktop-nav a {
	transition: color 0.2s ease;
}

.mobile-nav {
	transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}
```

### Animation Properties
- **Duration**: 0.2s for micro-interactions, 0.3s for navigation, 1s for page elements
- **Easing**: `ease` for standard, `ease-out` for entrance animations
- **Performance**: Use `transform` and `opacity` for smooth animations

## Component Styling

### Scoped Styles
- Use component-scoped styles in `<style>` blocks
- Avoid global CSS unless necessary
- Use CSS custom properties for theme consistency

### Class Naming
- Use **kebab-case** for CSS classes: `.mobile-nav-toggle`
- Use descriptive names: `.profile-container`, `.social-icons`
- Use BEM-like naming for complex components

### Box Shadows
```css
.profile-picture {
	box-shadow:
		0px 0px 3px 0px rgba(94, 230, 161, 0.2),
		0px 0px 6px 0px rgba(58, 167, 241, 0.2),
		0px 0px 8px 2px rgba(153, 153, 164, 0.2),
		0px 0px 10px 2px rgba(230, 138, 117, 0.2);
}
```

## Media Queries
```css
@media (max-width: 768px) {
	.profile-container {
		margin-top: -15vh;
	}
	
	.navbar {
		grid-template-columns: auto auto;
	}
}
```

## SVG Styling
- Use gradients for social icons
- Maintain consistent stroke-width: `1.5`
- Use `stroke-linecap="round"` and `stroke-linejoin="round"`

## Accessibility
- Ensure sufficient color contrast
- Use `aria-label` for interactive elements
- Provide focus states for keyboard navigation
- Use semantic HTML elements

## Performance
- Use `transform` instead of changing layout properties
- Minimize repaints and reflows
- Use `will-change` sparingly and remove after animation
- Optimize images and use appropriate formats